🔧 Technical Details
Architecture
Pure JavaScript - No external dependencies

CSS Custom Properties - Easy theming

Local Storage - Theme persistence

Client-side CSV parsing - No data leaves your browser

CSV Parsing
Handles quoted fields

Supports CRLF and LF line endings

Detects and handles BOM (Byte Order Mark)

Automatically trims whitespace

Data Types Detection
URL - Based on column name (link, url, website)

Date - Based on column name (date, created, updated)

Number - Based on column name and sample values

Text - Default type

Other - Fallback category

Performance
Pagination for large datasets

Efficient filtering and sorting

Minimal re-rendering

Lightweight DOM manipulation

