🛠️ Customization
Theming
The application supports dark and light themes. The theme preference is automatically saved.

Column Management
Set your own default visible columns

Reorder columns (drag and drop ready)

Toggle visibility for any column

Branding
The primary color (purple) can be customized in CSS by modifying:

css
--accent: #6d5bf6;
--accent-hover: #7e6ff9;
--accent-soft: rgba(109, 91, 246, 0.16);
📱 Responsive Design
Desktop - Full three-column layout

Tablet - Collapsible right panel

Mobile - Single column, sidebar hidden

